---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Moveroo | Moving & Transport Services">
	<section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-50 via-emerald-100 to-white py-24">
		<div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6 text-center">
			<p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-emerald-800">Services</p>
			<h1 class="mt-6 text-4xl font-semibold text-slate-900 md:text-5xl">Comprehensive solutions for every move</h1>
			<p class="mt-6 text-lg text-slate-600">
				Moveroo coordinates trusted carriers, removalists and logistics specialists across Australia. Whether you’re relocating a family home, moving vehicles, or need a customised transport plan, we tailor the service mix, schedule and communications around your needs.
			</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="bg-white py-24">
		<div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6">
			<div class="grid gap-10 md:grid-cols-3">
				<article class="flex flex-col gap-6 rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-8 shadow-lg shadow-slate-200/40">
					<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Car & Motorcycle Transport</h2>
					<p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-600">
						Door-to-door vehicle transport for cars, motorbikes, project builds and classic collections. Running or non-drivable options supported with winching and enclosed trailers available.
					</p>
					<ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-slate-600">
						<li class="flex items-start gap-3">
							<span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-500" aria-hidden="true"></span>
							<span>Nationwide carrier network with metro and regional coverage.</span>
						</li>
						<li class="flex items-start gap-3">
							<span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-500" aria-hidden="true"></span>
							<span>Condition reporting, insurance coordination and transit updates.</span>
						</li>
						<li class="flex items-start gap-3">
							<span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-500" aria-hidden="true"></span>
							<span>Flexible pickup windows plus expedited express options.</span>
						</li>
					</ul>
					<a
						class="inline-flex w-fit items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-emerald-500 px-5 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-emerald-700 transition hover:border-emerald-600 hover:text-emerald-900 focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-emerald-700"
						href="https://cars.moveroo.com.au"
						rel="noopener"
						target="_blank"
					>
						Get a free vehicle transport quote
					</a>
				</article>

				<article class="flex flex-col gap-6 rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-8 shadow-lg shadow-slate-200/40">
					<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Furniture Removalists & Backloading</h2>
					<p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-600">
						Full-service home moves managed end-to-end, from packing and loading to optional storage and unpacking. Backloading routes help optimise schedules and budgets for flexible dates.
					</p>
					<ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-slate-600">
						<li class="flex items-start gap-3">
							<span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-500" aria-hidden="true"></span>
							<span>Experienced removalist crews with protective materials supplied.</span>
						</li>
						<li class="flex items-start gap-3">
							<span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-500" aria-hidden="true"></span>
							<span>Inventory planning, staging and multi-stop coordination.</span>
						</li>
						<li class="flex items-start gap-3">
							<span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-500" aria-hidden="true"></span>
							<span>Backloading schedules for regional routes with transparent timelines.</span>
						</li>
					</ul>
					<a
						class="inline-flex w-fit items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-emerald-500 px-5 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-emerald-700 transition hover:border-emerald-600 hover:text-emerald-900 focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-emerald-700"
						href="https://removalists.moveroo.com.au/quote/household"
						rel="noopener"
						target="_blank"
					>
						Get a furniture move quote
					</a>
				</article>

				<article class="flex flex-col gap-6 rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-8 shadow-lg shadow-slate-200/40">
					<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Specialty & Oversized Transport</h2>
					<p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-600">
						Boats, caravans, trailers, industrial machinery and unique items that require bespoke handling. We match the right equipment, permits and escort services for complex moves.
					</p>
					<ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-slate-600">
						<li class="flex items-start gap-3">
							<span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-500" aria-hidden="true"></span>
							<span>Specialist towing and float solutions with full compliance support.</span>
						</li>
						<li class="flex items-start gap-3">
							<span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-500" aria-hidden="true"></span>
							<span>Large network of regional partners for agricultural and mining equipment.</span>
						</li>
						<li class="flex items-start gap-3">
							<span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-500" aria-hidden="true"></span>
							<span>Route planning, escort coordination and risk assessments handled by our team.</span>
						</li>
					</ul>
					<a
						class="inline-flex w-fit items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-emerald-500 px-5 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-emerald-700 transition hover:border-emerald-600 hover:text-emerald-900 focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-emerald-700"
						href="https://cars.moveroo.com.au/quote-types"
						rel="noopener"
						target="_blank"
					>
						Get a specialty transport quote
					</a>
				</article>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="border-y border-slate-200 bg-emerald-50/60 py-24">
		<div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6">
			<div class="md:grid md:grid-cols-[1.25fr_1fr] md:items-center md:gap-16">
				<div>
					<h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-slate-900">A guided process from enquiry to delivery</h2>
					<p class="mt-6 text-base leading-relaxed text-slate-600">
						Every move is different. We apply industry experience and regional knowledge to build a plan that stays in sync with your schedule.
					</p>
				</div>
				<ol class="mt-10 space-y-6 text-sm text-slate-600 md:mt-0">
					<li class="rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
						<p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-emerald-700">1. Discovery</p>
						<p class="mt-3 text-slate-700">Dedicated coordinators capture timelines, inventory, access requirements and any specialist handling instructions.</p>
					</li>
					<li class="rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
						<p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-emerald-700">2. Tailored plan</p>
						<p class="mt-3 text-slate-700">We curate the right partners, vehicles and team members, then provide a clear quote and itinerary.</p>
					</li>
					<li class="rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
						<p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-emerald-700">3. Managed delivery</p>
						<p class="mt-3 text-slate-700">Status updates at each milestone with proactive problem solving and post-move check-ins.</p>
					</li>
				</ol>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="bg-white py-20">
		<div class="mx-auto flex max-w-6xl flex-col gap-10 rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-50 via-white to-slate-100 px-6 py-12 text-center shadow-xl shadow-slate-200/60 md:flex-row md:items-center md:text-left">
			<div class="flex-1">
				<h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Ready to plan your move?</h2>
				<p class="mt-4 text-sm text-slate-600">
					Share the basics and we’ll align the right service mix, provide timelines and coordinate the next steps with you.
				</p>
			</div>
			<div class="flex flex-1 flex-col gap-4 md:items-end">
				<a class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-emerald-700 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-lg shadow-emerald-700/30 transition hover:bg-emerald-800 focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-emerald-800" href="/contact/#contact-form">
					Request a callback
				</a>
				<a class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-emerald-500 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-emerald-700 transition hover:border-emerald-600 hover:text-emerald-900 focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-emerald-700" href="https://removalists.moveroo.com.au/" rel="noopener" target="_blank">
					Book a moving quote
				</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>
